com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.impl.shardedjob

Interface ShardedJobState


  • public interface ShardedJobState
    Information about execution and progress of a sharded job. Undefined behavior results if any of the values (such as the return value of getSettings()) are mutated.
    Author:
    ohler@google.com (Christian Ohler)

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      int getActiveTaskCount()
      Returns the number of tasks or follow-up tasks that are currently active.

      Returns the time this job's state was last updated.

      Returns the execution settings of this job.

      Returns the time this job was started.
      Status getStatus()
      Returns whether this job is running, finished, etc.

      Returns the total number of tasks (not including follow-up tasks) that this job consists of.
